      ** Return Code
      ** Deal Type
      ** Work Trust Agreement
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
     C                   PARM                    PDealType
     C                   PARM                    PTrust
      ** OUTPUTS
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
      ** OK Flag
     C                   PARM                    FldNameArr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDArr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaArr
     C                   PARM                    OKTrust
 
